	Download and print the following <strong>PM Writing</strong> Text Type Fact Cards on A4 size paper. For best looking results, a colour printer is recommended. Once you have printed the Text Type Fact Cards, you may wish to laminate them for longevity.&nbsp;<br />
<br />
<h5>You can:</h5>
<ul>
    <li><span style="font-size: 12px;">pin them to your bulletin board</span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size: 12px;">tape them to your blackboard</span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size: 12px;">punch a hole in the top right hand corner of all the laminated sheets, tie/bind together and distribute among your small writing groups for reference</span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size: 12px;">print on to transparency sheets and display on your overhead projector.</span></li>
</ul>
